  "text": "In summary, our results imply that the better outcome for foreign word learning with enrichment can be explained by the recruitment of sensory and motor networks. This is in accordance with the multisensory learning theory [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . For teaching practice, the results suggest that using self-performed gestures during vocabulary learning is the better strategy for long-term vocabulary knowledge than the commonly practiced learning with pictures. ",
